    What is in the box?

  • Screenguard

    • Product Description

    FEDUS 3 in 1 Combo - Laptop Screen Guard, Keyboard Protector and Laptop Skin for 15.6 inch Laptop

    • THE HASSLE OF BUYING EACH COMPONENT FOR your laptop is gone with the new FEDUS laptop accessories combo kit. The Combo kit contains -

    1. One piece of laptop Skin (Reusable)
    2. One piece of Keyboard Protector
    3. One Piece of laptop screen guard

    Screen Protector

    • PROTECT SCREEN FROM SCRATCHES AND DUST: The screen guard protector is with superior performance to prevent scratches and dust when daily use.
    • ELECTROSTATIC ADSORPTION: Self-adhering (no glue) film attaches to the laptop screen. No residue leaves on your screen display when you remove it.
    • FILTERS OUT 99% OF UVB light from your screen or reflecting to your eyes, 99.99% Retina Clarity and Touchscreen Accuracy screen guard
    • 99% ULTRA-TRANSPARENCY makes the screen protector almost invisible, the oleophobic coating of matte protector reduces smudges and fingerprints greatly. You can clean your laptop screen with a simple wipe.

    Laptop Keyboard Protector Skin

    • ULTRA THIN DESIGN - with industry-leading 0.12mm/0.005-inch thickness, maximize to restore the original typing experience
    • PREVENT KEYBOARD - from coffee, tea, water, dust, and normal wear and tear damage your keyboard when daily use
    • FLEXIBLE AND WASHABLE - easy to apply and remove for cleaning or disinfection

    Laptop Skin Cover

    • DIMENSIINS: Of laptop sticker is 16.5" (41.91cm) x 11.50" (29.21cm) - Fits 13" 14" 15" & 15.6" wide screen laptops
    • TRIM: Easily trimmed down to fit smaller laptops under 15" with instructions
    • REMOVABLE: Easy to apply, easy to remove and no sticky residue when removed
    • MULTIFUNCTIONAL: Highly durable, dustproof, waterproof, non-fading reusable, gooey free adhesive and prevents abrasions and scratches.


    Warm Prompt

    • -If this is the first time you post screen protector, it will be better for you to buy 2 or more pieces in one time.
    • -We suggest you ask a professional to post the screen protector for you.
    • -About how to post screen protector, you can also search "how to install screen protectors" on YouTube.
    • - Note Shutdown state to reduce screen dust absorption To ensure that the screen without dust

    • Diagonal Length: 15.6 inches (39.6cm)
    • Width: 13.54 inches (34.39cm, 344mm)
    • Hight: 7.64 inches (19.4 cm, 194mm)
    • Screen Aspect Ratio: 16:9
    • Please allow the protector size with a tiny difference

    Make Sure is the right size BEFORE BUYING

    Correct measurement screen size, THIS MEASUREMENT IS CRITICAL

    1. Determine your screen type is a raised bezel or a flat front glass
    2. According to the screen type, measure your screen size
    3. Compare with screen protector size, screen guard size must be smaller than the screen

    • "RAISED BEZEL" SCREEN will have a raised plastic frame or bezel around the edges.
    • Measure the height and width of the screen's viewable area within bezel (excluding the raised frame)!

    • How to install
    • 1. Clean Screen from Dust, Smudges Using the Cleaning Cloth
    • 2. Remove the dust using the dust-absorber paper
    • 3. Pull the tab marked 1 and separate the protective film off the protector
    • 4. Gently apply the film to the screen starting from the top aligning the edges and work your away down the screen
    • 5. Gently scrape the installation card to squeeze out the bubbles
    • 6. When finished applying pull the tab marked 2 off
    Read more

    PERFECT DIMENSIONS AND FIT FOR ANY LAPTOP!

    This clean looking skin vinyl cover can mold to fit onto any different type or model of laptop - able to fit and scale to any of 13, 14, 15, 16.5 inch widescreen laptop, hp, macbook, pc, notebook, or chromebook. The dimensions of this vinyl skin cover are 15.5" x 11.5" and can easily adjust to any scale or sized laptop. Whether the brand is Acer, Asus, Dell, Apple, or Samsung, this type of vinyl skin and decal will be the perfect cover!

    • MULTIFUNCTIONAL: Highly durable, dustproof, waterproof, non-fading reusable, gooey free adhesive and prevents abrasions and scratches.

    Decal Sticker for 15.6 inch Laptop

    Laptop skins enable you and your device a unique look which are cool, trendy & personalized. These skins protect your device from dirt, minor scratches & dullness, increasing its life & re-sale value.

    Specification:

    • Dimensions (W x H): 15.5 inches x 11.5 inches
    • Compatibility: Most laptops with screen sizes ranging from 10" to 15.6"

    • Instructions for application
    • 1. Make sure your laptop is clean. Wipe it off with a soft cloth. The laptop should be free of dust, fat or grease - otherwise the laptop skin may not stick to your laptop as well as it's supposed to.
    • 2. Take the measurement of the applying area
    • 3. Trim the exact size before applying with a blade/scissors
    • 4. Align the laptop skin on your laptop, take care that you put it on straight and in the exact position that you want to place it
    • 5. Remove only one side of the liner from sheet, align to the applying surface and start attaching them slowly
    • 6. Proceed carefully with the use of a clean cloth and/or a plastic card (i.e. ATM card) to assure no air bubbles remain until the liner is removed.
    Read more

    Universal fit for all 14-17.3-inch laptop keyboards WITH NUMERIC KEYPAD

    Please measure your keyboard size first to avoid buying wrong

    • Dust and moisture accumulating on the laptop keyboard can affect the way it works. So, you need a robust protective layer like the 15.6-inch to 17.3-inch laptop silicone keyboard protector to protect the keyboard from such external conditions.
    • This cover also safeguards it from spilled food or drink. It also prevents leftover crumbs between the keys from hampering it’s working.

    Note:

    • Please measure your keyboard's size before purchase, please make sure that the following size is fit for your laptop, some laptop has larger number keypad is not fit with this

    • Material: Non-slip polyurethane
    • Easy to attach, remove and wash
    • Ultra-thin

    • Protection against food or drink spillage
